      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know what people say, but it doesn't feel real. i'm thousands of miles away from anyone who actually knows me. i look at my phone and there's nothing. i look at my apartment and it's just... empty. it feels like i've already vanished and i'm just waiting for my body to catch up. it's not even sad anymore, it just feels like a logical conclusion. like, why stay if there's no impact?",
