      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that \"reaching out\" feels like so much work for a payoff that isn't even there. like i'm trying to build a bridge to a place that doesn't exist. sometimes i think the world would just be a little bit quieter and more peaceful if people like me weren't constantly trying to take up space. like, does it really matter if one more person is gone from the equation? it feels like it would just be a net zero.",
